Dialogue: 0,0:00:02.97,0:00:07.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Suiyoubi No Downtown starts once more, thank you all for being here.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:07.77,0:00:11.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's kick things off with our first presenter, this person!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:15.54,0:00:19.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Hello everyone! - It's Jinnai Tomonori!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:19.67,0:00:21.97,Default,,0,0,0,,A question for you all!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:21.97,0:00:25.89,Default,,0,0,0,,3 years ago we did a project at Kuro-chan's place.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:25.89,0:00:31.11,Default,,0,0,0,,The "theory that a person could live under Kuro-chan's bed". Do you remember that? - Yes!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:31.11,0:00:33.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Quite a shocking project. - Indeed.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:33.83,0:00:38.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Back then we weren't exposed for 1.5 days, 39 hours! - Right.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:38.51,0:00:41.83,Default,,0,0,0,,At some point the hiding person had to go to the toilet ...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:41.83,0:00:46.57,Default,,0,0,0,,... where he did his business, but at the fear of getting exposed by the noise he didn't flush.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:46.57,0:00:52.95,Default,,0,0,0,,In the morning Kuro-chan saw his dump and he got exposed because of that.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:54.24,0:00:59.00,Default,,0,0,0,,It's probably scarier to find someone's dump than a person.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:59.00,0:01:03.38,Default,,0,0,0,,He might've thought he forgot to flush himself! -Like he had some kind of memory disorder!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:03.38,0:01:05.52,Default,,0,0,0,,But it didn't look like the shape he normally produces.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:05.52,0:01:10.32,Default,,0,0,0,,"I couldn't have made that", I know what you mean. - You do?!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:10.32,0:01:14.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Well this time our project takes us to Kuro-chan's home once more!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:14.76,0:01:18.56,Default,,0,0,0,,"Hide for money - at Kuro-chan's home"
Dialogue: 0,0:01:18.56,0:01:21.47,Default,,0,0,0,,Indeed! - "Hide for money"?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:21.77,0:01:26.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Kuro-chan actually moved to a new place on this show recently!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:26.03,0:01:28.87,Default,,0,0,0,,It's a lot more spacious than his last place.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:28.87,0:01:35.48,Default,,0,0,0,,What we did is to hide 10 TV personalities in his home while he was away. - 10?!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:35.48,0:01:38.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Wow! - Once Kuro-chan came home, ...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:38.63,0:01:41.99,Default,,0,0,0,,... we observed to see how long it'd take him to find them all.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:41.99,0:01:46.69,Default,,0,0,0,,Did he by chance figure it out after finding 10 people's worth of shit?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:46.69,0:01:47.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Not one of them would flush?!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:48.43,0:01:53.26,Default,,0,0,0,,You're about to witness "Hide for money - at Kuro-chan's home"!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:54.37,0:02:01.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Moreover, there's a segment about kids with a long way to school that's not covered in this fansub!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:17.37,0:02:21.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Hide for money - at Kuro-chan's home.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:21.54,0:02:25.10,Default,,0,0,0,,This time is all about hiding yourself at Kuro-chan's place!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:25.34,0:02:30.29,Default,,0,0,0,,We've gathered 10 TV personalities who seem like they might be good at hiding!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.31,0:02:41.55,Default,,0,0,0,,What's Takahashi Minami doing in a lineup like this?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:41.55,0:02:48.60,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm actually quite good friends with Kuro-chan, so that's the reason I'm here!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.60,0:02:53.66,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm also here as a friend. - We're both here for that reason!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.20,0:02:58.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Including these two, who are Kuro-chan's friends, ...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.11,0:03:01.34,Default,,0,0,0,,... everyone's average height is 158cm!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.11,0:03:01.34,Comments,,0,0,0,,They're all quite short!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.34,0:03:05.84,Default,,0,0,0,,10 contestants who've all cleared their PCR tests!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.40,0:03:10.44,Default,,0,0,0,,The biggest light weight of all of them is ...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.44,0:03:14.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Me, Seiga! I weigh 39kg, ...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.83,0:03:18.78,Default,,0,0,0,,... so I want to make the most of that and do my best! Count on me!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.03,0:03:22.15,Default,,0,0,0,,He has a face that could beat Inada (Naoki).
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.71,0:03:26.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Meanwhile, the home owner Kuro-chan ...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.56,0:03:31.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Q: Describe your life in a few words.\NK: "From now on"
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.80,0:03:33.31,Comments,,0,0,0,,Doing some kind of interview?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.14,0:03:36.92,Default,,0,0,0,,He's taking part in a fake interview.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.60,0:03:38.15,Comments,,0,0,0,,What kind of answer is "from now on"?! - Seriously.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.92,0:03:46.11,Default,,0,0,0,,And so the contestants head into Kuro-chan's place that's been equipped with 19 hidden cameras.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.24,0:03:46.11,Comments,,0,0,0,,What's that supposed to mean? "From now on".
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.34,0:03:49.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Everyone, please hide!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.11,0:03:50.73,Comments,,0,0,0,,Still messy as always! \N- That even his new place would turn out like this.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.17,0:03:58.94,Default,,0,0,0,,By the way, the contestants will earn 10 yen for each second of hiding until they're found!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.39,0:04:05.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Kuro-chan will arrive in an hour, so please hide before then!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.17,0:04:07.15,Comments,,0,0,0,,That's his NEW place?! \N- Clean the place! - It's filthy!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.13,0:04:08.33,Default,,0,0,0,,The toilet is filthy!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.33,0:04:12.60,Default,,0,0,0,,This place is ... - A mess!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.47,0:04:14.40,Comments,,0,0,0,,He really doesn't change.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.86,0:04:18.74,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm thinking of hiding among all this cardboard. It seems like a blind spot.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.26,0:04:27.08,Default,,0,0,0,,And so he hides by ripping a hole into the cardboard boxes that have been sitting here since Kuro-chan moved in.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.26,0:04:30.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Looks pretty good! - Right?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.57,0:04:32.34,Comments,,0,0,0,,Pretty good spot.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.31,0:04:32.34,Default,,0,0,0,,They say "it's hard to see what's under your nose".
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.34,0:04:35.91,Default,,0,0,0,,The closest place would be here, right? Since he'll sit there.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.91,0:04:42.00,Default,,0,0,0,,If I hide back here ...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.00,0:04:46.34,Default,,0,0,0,,... I'll be able to know what he's up to, because I'm so close!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.34,0:04:48.63,Default,,0,0,0,,That could work in my favor.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.63,0:04:53.01,Default,,0,0,0,,I've got this one in the bag! Money, here I come!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.07,0:04:53.01,Comments,,0,0,0,,Ah, very good!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.46,0:04:58.65,Default,,0,0,0,,One by one, each of them decides on their hiding spot.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.71,0:05:03.80,Default,,0,0,0,,It starts when Kuro-chan gets back, so please do your best!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.54,0:05:06.99,Comments,,0,0,0,,Under the sink, under the bed ... - The apartment isn't so bad.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.99,0:05:09.38,Comments,,0,0,0,,Quite spacious!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.17,0:05:13.53,Default,,0,0,0,,And then ... the home owner returns.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.26,0:05:19.97,Default,,0,0,0,,"Hide for money - at Kuro-chan's place" starts!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.74,0:05:20.89,Comments,,0,0,0,,Clean up, dammit! \N- Yes, it's a new place!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.09,0:05:29.23,Default,,0,0,0,,As soon as he gets home, he starts digging into the bento he got at his shoot ...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.23,0:05:34.94,Default,,0,0,0,,... as well as a convenience store meal. It's double portions for him.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.94,0:05:37.63,Default,,0,0,0,,And then ...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.63,0:05:41.80,Default,,0,0,0,,"Breakfast & lunch in one! Grated yam soba & onion soup!"
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.23,0:05:44.86,Comments,,0,0,0,,That's not true!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.86,0:05:49.43,Comments,,0,0,0,,He just can't stop lying!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.80,0:05:45.89,Default,,0,0,0,,"Living the healthy life-dashiiiiin~!"
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.23,0:05:51.57,Default,,0,0,0,,He doesn't mention the yakiniku bento, and falls back into the habit of lying in his tweets.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.37,0:05:59.91,Default,,0,0,0,,He also doesn't notice the contestant who's hidden only 2m from where he sits.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.33,0:05:59.91,Comments,,0,0,0,,He's moving around! - This is bad!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.34,0:06:04.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Kuro-chan is fully immersed in his bento.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.80,0:06:08.25,Default,,0,0,0,,But then ...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.71,0:06:08.25,Comments,,0,0,0,,He doesn't notice! \N- How's he so carefree?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.09,0:06:14.42,Default,,0,0,0,,The curtain moves in an unnatural way.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.20,0:06:18.80,Default,,0,0,0,,And then ...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.29,0:06:20.60,Comments,,0,0,0,,Now he's noticed it!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.29,0:06:23.75,Comments,,0,0,0,,But you wouldn't expect someone to be there!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.75,0:06:27.47,Default,,0,0,0,,Kuro-chan sensed that something was off.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.23,0:06:31.11,Default,,0,0,0,,And in that moment ... !
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.86,0:06:36.80,Comments,,0,0,0,,What? Some kind of noise?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.26,0:06:43.92,Default,,0,0,0,,A big mistake - he dropped his phone!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.94,0:06:48.09,Comments,,0,0,0,,What's wrong with you? - Bad move, Wes-P.\N- He just dropped his phone?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.34,0:06:52.26,Comments,,0,0,0,,Those thighs piss me off!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.26,0:06:56.65,Comments,,0,0,0,,Not one milimeter of thigh gap!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.86,0:06:58.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Kuro-chan instinctively takes a step back.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.44,0:07:02.51,Comments,,0,0,0,,He seems frightened. - Yes, he can't speak!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.51,0:07:05.49,Comments,,0,0,0,,He's not even asking "Who's there?".
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.37,0:07:09.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Although he's frightened, he slowly comes closer.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.71,0:07:12.71,Comments,,0,0,0,,It moved again!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.14,0:07:18.05,Comments,,0,0,0,,He wanted a blind spot, but it's no use.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.89,0:07:23.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Ah, I knew it!! There's someone there!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.00,0:07:28.87,Default,,0,0,0,,After 15min 26sec, Wes-P has been secured.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.97,0:07:32.83,Comments,,0,0,0,,Wes-P, that was no good. - Big blunder on your part.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.17,0:07:32.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Eh, who are you?!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.83,0:07:36.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Ugh, so soon ... - "So soon", what's that supposed to mean?!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.57,0:07:40.23,Default,,0,0,0,,Shit. - Eh, what are you on about?!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.03,0:07:43.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Nice to meet you. - Uhm, you too ... ?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.94,0:07:46.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh man ... - What is this?!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.26,0:07:50.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Why's someone in my home I don't even know?! - This sucks.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.17,0:07:52.83,Default,,0,0,0,,It ended so soon. - What's that supposed to mean?!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.83,0:07:56.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Why were you here anyway?! HEY?! - So frustrating.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.63,0:07:58.80,Default,,0,0,0,,W-who was that?!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.80,0:08:00.89,Default,,0,0,0,,Some dude I don't know was here!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.89,0:08:03.80,Default,,0,0,0,,What kinda prank is this? Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.06,0:08:06.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you with Wednesday('s Downtown)?!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.54,0:08:09.91,Default,,0,0,0,,But hang on, he just left!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.91,0:08:14.31,Default,,0,0,0,,Wes-P, unrecognized by Kuro-chan, is headed for ...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.60,0:08:21.86,Default,,0,0,0,,... a jail up on the roof of the building.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.29,0:08:26.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Eh, what is this? Is it over? Hey!!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.91,0:08:29.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Come out for the reveal already! What is this?!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.60,0:08:33.83,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't get what's going on! Come and do the reveal!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.83,0:08:37.83,Default,,0,0,0,,But our "Hide for money" has only just begun.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.83,0:08:42.44,Default,,0,0,0,,There's no way we'd reveal it this early on.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.00,0:08:46.91,Default,,0,0,0,,10 minutes pass.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.20,0:08:49.91,Default,,0,0,0,,And then ...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.09,0:08:56.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Perhaps he thought there were hints behind the curtains?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.69,0:09:00.69,Default,,0,0,0,,Kuro-chan investigates all the curtains.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.09,0:09:02.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Ah, this is bad!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.86,0:09:05.86,Default,,0,0,0,,And then ...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.31,0:09:05.86,Comments,,0,0,0,,The cardboard!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.86,0:09:09.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Eh! There's someone here! Right?! There totally is!!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.03,0:09:11.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Right? Who are you?!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.86,0:09:16.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Uwah, I knew it! There IS someone! Who are you?!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.91,0:09:19.98,Default,,0,0,0,,BICSMALLN's Chiro has been secured.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.31,0:09:23.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Hang on, you're that Choro guy, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.83,0:09:26.03,Comments,,0,0,0,,Choro? His name's Chiro!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.29,0:09:27.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Kuro-chan isn't very familiar with entertainers.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.86,0:09:31.31,Default,,0,0,0,,How many are there?! Are there still more?!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.20,0:09:38.96,Default,,0,0,0,,And so at last he sets out on his journey as ... hunter!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.26,0:09:42.38,Default,,0,0,0,,And then ...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.37,0:09:42.87,Comments,,0,0,0,,If he's going like this, he'll search under the bed next.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.37,0:09:46.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Ah, there's someone!! I knew it!! Right there!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.71,0:09:51.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Who are you?! - Ugh, I figured I'd be fine here.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.73,0:09:53.57,Comments,,0,0,0,,Once he knew something was up, he was bound to search there.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.00,0:09:54.34,Default,,0,0,0,,What are you on about?!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.34,0:09:57.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Shit, that was so soon ...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.63,0:10:00.35,Default,,0,0,0,,What are you cursing for?!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.63,0:10:03.35,Default,,0,0,0,,I really thought I could pull it off.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.35,0:10:07.03,Default,,0,0,0,,What's your point, seriously?!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.51,0:10:11.54,Default,,0,0,0,,And with this, Kuro-chan follows the contestant.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.86,0:10:13.97,Default,,0,0,0,,And what he finds is ...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.97,0:10:16.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Eh ... ?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.54,0:10:19.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Wh-what are you doing?!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.70,0:10:23.47,Default,,0,0,0,,What is this? What are you guys doing here?!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.47,0:10:27.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Was this especially set up for Kuro-chan? - Yes, just for him!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.80,0:10:32.20,Default,,0,0,0,,While the hunter has left his post ...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.20,0:10:36.77,Default,,0,0,0,,I need to stretch myself a little ... !
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.77,0:10:40.31,Comments,,0,0,0,,Is Takamina doing fine?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.97,0:10:40.06,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm a bit thirsty.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.00,0:10:45.58,Comments,,0,0,0,,Is that really ok? \N- He'll come back!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.31,0:10:44.77,Default,,0,0,0,,Maybe I'll help myself to some water. This one still looks sealed, so I guess it's fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.54,0:10:49.77,Default,,0,0,0,,The contestants use the time to catch a breather!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.40,0:10:53.00,Default,,0,0,0,,But this is the roof of my building!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.00,0:10:55.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you doing "Run for money"?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.06,0:10:57.24,Default,,0,0,0,,You are, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.24,0:11:00.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Enough already! I figured it out, enough!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.71,0:11:03.14,Default,,0,0,0,,What's wrong with you?!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.14,0:11:09.74,Default,,0,0,0,,At last Kuro-chan figured out that this is a parody of "Run of money".
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.80,0:11:15.40,Comments,,0,0,0,,He's back! - This is bad!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.80,0:11:20.55,Comments,,0,0,0,,What are you doing? \N- What's wrong with that guy?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.40,0:11:17.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, who's there?!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.11,0:11:20.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Who are you?! I know you're there! I found you!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.34,0:11:23.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Ah, shit.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.20,0:11:27.94,Comments,,0,0,0,,He was being too reckless!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.94,0:11:30.67,Default,,0,0,0,,You're doing "Run for money", right? - Ugh, shit.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.67,0:11:33.54,Default,,0,0,0,,How terrifying would it have been if he'd found Seiga first.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.83,0:11:38.75,Default,,0,0,0,,At this point, 1 hour has passed since the project began.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.54,0:11:43.39,Default,,0,0,0,,Only the 6 people seen here still remain.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.46,0:11:46.86,Default,,0,0,0,,But then ...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.86,0:11:51.73,Default,,0,0,0,,My manager gave me this earlier, what is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.00,0:11:56.26,Default,,0,0,0,,He said "Use it at your next job". So he wants me to wear it?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.51,0:11:58.74,Default,,0,0,0,,That's right. For his "next job", ...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.74,0:12:06.68,Default,,0,0,0,,... in other words, for THIS job, he was given a black suit just like the one hunters wear.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.97,0:12:09.09,Default,,0,0,0,,I should wear this, right? Right?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.09,0:12:10.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Are there still more?!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.29,0:12:17.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Kuro-chan changes his clothes as he keeps voicing complaints about everything.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.54,0:12:21.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Now put on these sunglasses ...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.77,0:12:24.46,Comments,,0,0,0,,Why'd you wear them at home?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.80,0:12:24.46,Default,,0,0,0,,There's even a camera attached on the side!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.74,0:12:27.00,Default,,0,0,0,,I really look like a hunter!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.31,0:12:30.50,Default,,0,0,0,,A unique kind of hunter.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.29,0:12:37.87,Default,,0,0,0,,A hunter he may be, albeit more reminiscent of Umibozu from City Hunter.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.87,0:12:41.21,Default,,0,0,0,,How many are there? I guess I gotta search for them?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.46,0:12:44.46,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll find you! I will!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.17,0:12:48.29,Comments,,0,0,0,,He's found 4 already. - But he doesn't know how many are left.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.74,0:12:48.29,Default,,0,0,0,,I already caught this one.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.57,0:12:51.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Next would be ...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.51,0:12:55.32,Default,,0,0,0,,This would be the main room, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.00,0:13:03.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Here, my walk-in closet.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.66,0:13:08.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Eh, what's that? Did something fall off the rack?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.00,0:13:14.71,Default,,0,0,0,,I found you! I totally did!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.94,0:13:16.74,Default,,0,0,0,,What the hell!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.74,0:13:20.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Gimme a break! - It's Makino Suteteko!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.54,0:13:23.87,Default,,0,0,0,,I was sure you wouldn't find me! - You're number 5!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.87,0:13:26.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Whatever. - I found you-shiiiyo!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.51,0:13:31.09,Default,,0,0,0,,Having found 5 people, Kuro-chan does ...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.37,0:13:34.80,Default,,0,0,0,,That should be everyone, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.09,0:13:37.37,Default,,0,0,0,,That was easy-peasy.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.63,0:13:41.89,Default,,0,0,0,,Ok~! The staff just needs to show up now.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.89,0:13:44.54,Default,,0,0,0,,I got all 5, bingo~!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.11,0:13:49.17,Default,,0,0,0,,No part of him thinks there'd be 10 people hidden in total.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.17,0:13:52.11,Default,,0,0,0,,He mistakenly thinks 5 would be a nice round number.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.17,0:13:56.83,Default,,0,0,0,,With that, his search comes to an end.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.10,0:13:58.77,Comments,,0,0,0,,Clean up the place! - Seriously.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.34,0:14:00.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Someone save us. - Someone, please!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.57,0:14:03.46,Default,,0,0,0,,That's right!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.46,0:14:08.00,Default,,0,0,0,,If someone can rescue the members on the roof without being caught by Kuro-chan ...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.00,0:14:14.40,Default,,0,0,0,,... they can earn a bonus of 50 000 yen, as an extra rule!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.31,0:14:21.94,Default,,0,0,0,,And so this man, who was hiding on the veranda, is making his move.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.94,0:14:24.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Alright, I'll head up to save them!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.26,0:14:28.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Chance is coming for us!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.11,0:14:34.14,Default,,0,0,0,,He enters the apartment from the veranda via the window, ...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.80,0:14:34.14,Comments,,0,0,0,,He'll find you like this, isn't this dangerous?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.14,0:14:36.83,Default,,0,0,0,,... and heads to the roof.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.14,0:14:36.83,Comments,,0,0,0,,Oh, he made it!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.86,0:14:44.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Ah, Chance is here! Chance has come!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.54,0:14:46.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you~!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.37,0:14:50.31,Default,,0,0,0,,However, only 1 person can be rescued at a time!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.31,0:14:55.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Please save me! - Please save me!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.00,0:15:00.37,Default,,0,0,0,,He worked hard at King Of Conte, so I'll pick Sakai! - Ah, thank you!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.37,0:15:03.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Come out! - Come back for us as well!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.94,0:15:09.19,Default,,0,0,0,,With this, Chance Oshiro earns a 50 000 yen bonus!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.46,0:15:17.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Unnoticed by an inattentive Kuro-chan, Chance makes it back out to the veranda.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.17,0:15:24.09,Default,,0,0,0,,Sakai also ...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.90,0:15:24.09,Comments,,0,0,0,,The veranda seems dangerous.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.46,0:15:34.94,Default,,0,0,0,,... heads back underneath the bed, thinking there's no way he'd search the same place twice.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.17,0:15:39.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Is the staff still not coming out? Hey!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.43,0:15:49.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Eh? Is there someone there?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.07,0:15:46.26,Comments,,0,0,0,,Ah! Another phone?!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.71,0:15:54.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Eh, wasn't there a sound just now? Is there someone?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.17,0:15:57.37,Default,,0,0,0,,Where was it? I heard some kind of bang.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.37,0:15:59.89,Default,,0,0,0,,I think it was back here!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.37,0:16:05.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Sakai turned Kuro-chan's hunter switch back on!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.66,0:16:08.14,Default,,0,0,0,,And then ...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.86,0:16:11.14,Default,,0,0,0,,There's someone!!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.80,0:16:23.93,Default,,0,0,0,,Sakai repays his rescue from the roof by getting him caught.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.47,0:16:19.00,Comments,,0,0,0,,He got Chance caught with that!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.71,0:16:27.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Are there still more of you?!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.49,0:16:33.94,Default,,0,0,0,,With this, Kuro-chan realizes there are more than 5 people, ...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.94,0:16:37.75,Default,,0,0,0,,... and he resumes his search.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.65,0:16:47.17,Default,,0,0,0,,There's someone! - Kyah~! - Who's screaming?!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.43,0:16:49.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Eh, Takamina?!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.14,0:16:51.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Why'd you have to find me?!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.60,0:16:56.47,Default,,0,0,0,,What-, wait ... why is Takamina in my home? - Seriously, why?! You're so cruel!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.47,0:17:00.17,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't get what's going on but you can't just come in here with a bunch of comedians!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.17,0:17:02.55,Default,,0,0,0,,After that ...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.40,0:17:07.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Uwah! Another one!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.34,0:17:11.57,Default,,0,0,0,,You found me ... - Ah, it's Yabe!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.57,0:17:14.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Screw you! - You can't say that to the home owner!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.92,0:17:18.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Screw you! - You can't speak badly of people!!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.20,0:17:20.76,Default,,0,0,0,,You make me sick! - Don't say that!!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.49,0:17:33.97,Default,,0,0,0,,[These subs are brought to you voluntarily, without the support of any of the sponsors listed up there]
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.74,0:17:37.91,Default,,0,0,0,,3 hours have passed since we started.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.09,0:17:42.65,Default,,0,0,0,,The 3 listed here still remain.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.10,0:17:47.93,Comments,,0,0,0,,Sakai is doing well! - You'd think he'd be out by now.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.54,0:17:45.76,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll look around the kitchen.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.76,0:17:50.00,Default,,0,0,0,,As Kuro-chan appears to investigate the kitchen ...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.26,0:17:54.77,Default,,0,0,0,,... the man under the bed makes his move.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.99,0:17:54.77,Comments,,0,0,0,,He's coming out? - Something he wants to do?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.77,0:17:58.11,Default,,0,0,0,,In order to prepare for the long term, ...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.11,0:18:02.10,Default,,0,0,0,,... he grabs a blanket, pillow, ...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.00,0:18:03.73,Comments,,0,0,0,,Gotta check the smell.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.73,0:18:07.89,Comments,,0,0,0,,Those make noise!! - He's gonna come!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.37,0:18:06.94,Default,,0,0,0,,... potato chips, gummi candy, and ...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.94,0:18:08.86,Default,,0,0,0,,It's so cold!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.86,0:18:14.06,Default,,0,0,0,,He even grabs some warm clothes!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.06,0:18:16.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Much warmer~!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.74,0:18:19.87,Default,,0,0,0,,And then ...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.29,0:18:23.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Koishida? - Yeah?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.03,0:18:26.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Right now I think you can grab anything you need.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.20,0:18:28.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Sure seems like it.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.46,0:18:35.29,Default,,0,0,0,,After gaining this information from his neighbor Sakai ...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.00,0:18:31.46,Comments,,0,0,0,,Ah, he was there?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.29,0:18:41.03,Default,,0,0,0,,... Koishida emerges from his closet for the first time in 3 hours!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.43,0:18:44.89,Default,,0,0,0,,Was that a noise just now?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.91,0:18:48.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Was there a noise? Hey, is someone there?!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.98,0:18:51.95,Default,,0,0,0,,It really turned into "Run for money"! - Hide quickly!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.54,0:18:55.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, where are you? Where?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.34,0:18:58.26,Default,,0,0,0,,There was a noise just now!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.26,0:19:06.77,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm sure there was a noise, it was pretty loud!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.77,0:19:10.83,Comments,,0,0,0,,It's wide open!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.13,0:19:16.97,Comments,,0,0,0,,But it's a small closet, it seems unlikely someone would be in there.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.90,0:19:03.26,Comments,,0,0,0,,He'll be found like that!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.40,0:19:20.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Did I leave it half open like this?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.91,0:19:25.31,Default,,0,0,0,,It feels somewhat warm ...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.89,0:19:30.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Found you! I got you!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.00,0:19:34.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, come on! - I found you~!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.61,0:19:37.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you Koishida?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.70,0:19:37.59,Comments,,0,0,0,,Sorry, Sumire!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.61,0:19:41.86,Default,,0,0,0,,They got your (Sumire's) dad. - Daddy!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.34,0:19:46.40,Default,,0,0,0,,And so only 2 remain.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.66,0:19:50.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Moreover, since it's past 4 pm ...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.46,0:19:53.63,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't have much time before my next job, so ...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.63,0:19:59.06,Default,,0,0,0,,... I need to change and leave! Got it? I gotta go!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.57,0:20:05.89,Default,,0,0,0,,Kuro-chan might be going somewhere, but the project will continue until everyone is caught.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.89,0:20:10.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Damn, my apartment's all messy now!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.97,0:20:12.64,Comments,,0,0,0,,It was messy from the start!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.37,0:20:14.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Have fun at work!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.74,0:20:19.89,Default,,0,0,0,,Here the remaining two can catch a breather at last. But ...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.57,0:20:23.97,Default,,0,0,0,,You're here, right?! - Woah, he's back!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.67,0:20:25.70,Comments,,0,0,0,,Eh, that's scary!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.97,0:20:26.51,Default,,0,0,0,,You're here, right? I know you are!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.80,0:20:30.91,Default,,0,0,0,,The way he goes about it is scary! - Hey, hey, hey!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:30.91,0:20:33.60,Default,,0,0,0,,You're here, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.91,0:20:36.97,Default,,0,0,0,,Getting dangerous ... !
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.31,0:20:41.76,Default,,0,0,0,,I really gotta go, you know?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:41.76,0:20:46.45,Default,,0,0,0,,I do have to go, even though I'm not sure I really have work tonight.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.45,0:20:50.02,Default,,0,0,0,,But I'm short on time, so I'll head out now!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:52.17,0:20:53.63,Default,,0,0,0,,What was that?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.63,0:20:55.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Did he leave?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:55.40,0:20:57.57,Default,,0,0,0,,This time he really left, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.57,0:21:01.94,Default,,0,0,0,,He left, right? Then so will I. Here I go.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:56.07,0:21:00.30,Comments,,0,0,0,,No, wait a bit more!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:02.60,0:21:05.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Uwah! - Thank gosh it's you.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:05.61,0:21:07.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank goodness.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:07.83,0:21:11.45,Default,,0,0,0,,He really did leave, right? - Yeah!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:11.86,0:21:13.52,Default,,0,0,0,,And then ...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:13.52,0:21:17.93,Default,,0,0,0,,I think he might not be back for another 3 hours. - 3 hours?!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:18.69,0:21:24.17,Default,,0,0,0,,That's according to Kikuchi, who works with Kuro-chan every day.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:24.17,0:21:28.29,Default,,0,0,0,,We're basically free to do anything for these 3 hours.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:28.29,0:21:30.37,Default,,0,0,0,,And so ...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:30.37,0:21:32.81,Default,,0,0,0,,Shall we order food?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:33.26,0:21:34.77,Default,,0,0,0,,Hello ... ?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:35.00,0:21:37.65,Default,,0,0,0,,They order pizza.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:38.11,0:21:40.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Wow, this is great!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:40.86,0:21:44.05,Default,,0,0,0,,They fill their stomachs to prepare themselves for the long haul.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:44.60,0:21:47.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Meanwhile, on the roof.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:43.53,0:21:46.43,Comments,,0,0,0,,You sure he won't come back?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:47.05,0:21:50.57,Default,,0,0,0,,I actually have work after this, so ... - Eh?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:51.26,0:21:57.69,Default,,0,0,0,,Takahashi Minami, the only TV personality here who's actually in demand, retires from the game.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:58.29,0:22:03.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Now 3 hours have passed since Kuro-chan left for his work.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:03.17,0:22:06.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's get back to it again. Thanks for everything!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:07.83,0:22:14.09,Default,,0,0,0,,They head back like employees staying at a business hotel on a work trip.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:14.63,0:22:18.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Each of them goes back to their old position.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:16.73,0:22:21.30,Comments,,0,0,0,,The bath ... - He'll be found for sure!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:18.97,0:22:22.96,Default,,0,0,0,,It's tight around my stomach, I ate too much!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:23.20,0:22:28.00,Default,,0,0,0,,This bath is actually quite pleasant.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:23.83,0:22:28.00,Comments,,0,0,0,,The bath's dangerous, Kikuchi!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:28.93,0:22:32.47,Comments,,0,0,0,,He hasn't even searched it yet.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:28.00,0:22:30.17,Default,,0,0,0,,He's even got manga.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:30.71,0:22:33.54,Default,,0,0,0,,7 hours since the start.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:33.54,0:22:38.01,Default,,0,0,0,,They've gotten fairly used to their life in hiding.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:38.34,0:22:41.03,Default,,0,0,0,,But then ...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:40.43,0:22:41.87,Comments,,0,0,0,,He's back!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:41.87,0:22:44.73,Comments,,0,0,0,,Very slowly.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:43.37,0:22:48.63,Default,,0,0,0,,The home owner returns, on tiptoes like a burglar!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:46.93,0:22:53.54,Comments,,0,0,0,,At his own home! - I get how he feels though.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:53.54,0:22:55.80,Default,,0,0,0,,And then ...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:55.80,0:23:00.89,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm back, hear me?! I'm back!!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:58.00,0:23:03.63,Comments,,0,0,0,,Why's he announcing himself?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:03.63,0:23:11.69,Default,,0,0,0,,Hm, where are you? Where might you be? I'm back! Did you wait for me?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:11.69,0:23:13.89,Default,,0,0,0,,He startled me ... - Did I startle you?!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:13.89,0:23:17.77,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm back! The home owner has returned!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:17.77,0:23:19.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey there~!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:21.29,0:23:26.91,Default,,0,0,0,,I came back dashing once my broadcast was over! Hear me?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:23.67,0:23:26.91,Comments,,0,0,0,,"Dashing"
Dialogue: 0,0:23:27.14,0:23:33.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Where are you? Let's put an end to this alright?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:33.37,0:23:36.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Seriously, where are you? Where?!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:38.14,0:23:41.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Scary! - Why's he so agitated?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:41.60,0:23:44.54,Default,,0,0,0,,We really need to end this now! Seriously!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:44.54,0:23:49.65,Default,,0,0,0,,If we don't end this soon I'm gonna lose my freaking mind!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:52.69,0:23:56.51,Default,,0,0,0,,In a complete reversal from the cat burglar style he showed at first ...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:56.51,0:24:01.59,Default,,0,0,0,,... Kuro-chan runs around from room to room in a bizarre state.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:02.00,0:24:05.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Once I wear this I'll be in hunter mode!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:06.23,0:24:08.63,Default,,0,0,0,,There are still more left, aren't there?!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:08.63,0:24:12.06,Default,,0,0,0,,He once again picks up his search!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:09.50,0:24:13.30,Comments,,0,0,0,,The bath's dangerous!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:12.06,0:24:17.20,Default,,0,0,0,,There's still a place I haven't searched yet.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:18.83,0:24:23.26,Default,,0,0,0,,This is bad, he'll come in here ... - A place I haven't searched~!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:29.09,0:24:30.65,Default,,0,0,0,,You're in trouble!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:33.06,0:24:34.63,Default,,0,0,0,,And then ...
Dialogue: 0,0:24:34.63,0:24:36.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Who's in here?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:36.71,0:24:41.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Uwah, shit! - Kikuchi? Eh, Kikuchi?!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:42.03,0:24:49.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Wanwan-nyannyan's Kikuchi is secured after 7h 12min.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:49.74,0:24:53.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Now I've found everyone, right? All 10?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:53.54,0:24:58.08,Default,,0,0,0,,I've found everyone! ALL TEN OF THEM!!!!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:58.08,0:25:03.37,Default,,0,0,0,,Of course Kuro-chan doesn't know about the rescue rule.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:03.37,0:25:06.69,Default,,0,0,0,,He's convinced this means it's over.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:06.13,0:25:09.97,Comments,,0,0,0,,He's just casually eating something.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:07.91,0:25:10.46,Default,,0,0,0,,The staff still won't show for some reason.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:10.77,0:25:17.37,Default,,0,0,0,,In that case ... I've gotten all sweaty, so I'll take a bath.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:17.63,0:25:21.83,Default,,0,0,0,,He's taking a bath. That's my chance!
Dialogue: 0,0:25:24.89,0:25:26.74,Default,,0,0,0,,He's in the bath!
Dialogue: 0,0:25:24.89,0:25:28.20,Comments,,0,0,0,,Zero privacy!
Dialogue: 0,0:25:27.29,0:25:30.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Taking this chance, Sakai goes and ...
Dialogue: 0,0:25:30.45,0:25:36.37,Default,,0,0,0,,Sakai's coming! - He'll rescue us, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:25:36.97,0:25:38.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Aaaah, nice!
Dialogue: 0,0:25:41.51,0:25:43.49,Default,,0,0,0,,Who are you picking?
Dialogue: 0,0:25:43.49,0:25:46.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Chance! To repay you for earlier!
Dialogue: 0,0:25:46.30,0:25:49.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Sweet! - I'm still in the game because of you!
Dialogue: 0,0:25:49.57,0:25:54.64,Default,,0,0,0,,To thank him for rescuing him once, he rescues Chance.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:55.40,0:26:01.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Kuro-chan is defenseless as he's still occupied with shower time.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:01.60,0:26:06.51,Default,,0,0,0,,While he's busy, they both make their way back to the apartment.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:06.89,0:26:10.95,Default,,0,0,0,,As their hiding spots, they pick ...
Dialogue: 0,0:26:10.95,0:26:13.54,Default,,0,0,0,,That was Takahashi Minami's spot!
Dialogue: 0,0:26:16.20,0:26:20.97,Default,,0,0,0,,Chance heads into the closet Takahashi Minami was hiding in earlier.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:20.97,0:26:24.54,Default,,0,0,0,,It smells like Minami~!
Dialogue: 0,0:26:24.54,0:26:27.93,Comments,,0,0,0,,What are you talking about?
Dialogue: 0,0:26:25.34,0:26:30.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Sakai on the other hand heads back underneath the bed.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:30.63,0:26:33.77,Default,,0,0,0,,I rescued Chance!
Dialogue: 0,0:26:34.66,0:26:38.95,Default,,0,0,0,,9h 30min have passed since the start of this project.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:38.95,0:26:41.95,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm about to get ready for bed after this ...
Dialogue: 0,0:26:41.95,0:26:44.99,Default,,0,0,0,,... so is the staff really not gonna show up?
Dialogue: 0,0:26:44.99,0:26:48.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Ah, wait! Isn't everyone on the roof still?
Dialogue: 0,0:26:48.86,0:26:52.63,Comments,,0,0,0,,They'll be exposed! Oh-oh.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:52.63,0:26:55.60,Comments,,0,0,0,,Ah, no one's there!
Dialogue: 0,0:26:49.91,0:26:52.63,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll go up there and ask them!
Dialogue: 0,0:26:55.60,0:26:57.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Eh ... ?
Dialogue: 0,0:27:01.09,0:27:04.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Eh? They're gone?
Dialogue: 0,0:27:00.20,0:27:04.71,Comments,,0,0,0,,He must think it's over.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:04.71,0:27:08.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Did they all go home? What's the meaning of this?
Dialogue: 0,0:27:09.17,0:27:10.69,Default,,0,0,0,,As a matter of fact ...
Dialogue: 0,0:27:10.69,0:27:16.57,Default,,0,0,0,,... when Chance was rescued the scheduled time for the shoot was already exceeded ...
Dialogue: 0,0:27:16.57,0:27:21.22,Default,,0,0,0,,... so the group on the roof dissolved and left.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:22.63,0:27:25.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Does this mean it's over?
Dialogue: 0,0:27:25.06,0:27:28.54,Default,,0,0,0,,There's no one here, right? Did they go home?
Dialogue: 0,0:27:28.80,0:27:33.37,Default,,0,0,0,,Where are they going with this? Why does no one tell me stuff, seriously.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:33.74,0:27:39.54,Default,,0,0,0,,At this point Kuro-chan is convinced the shoot is over.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:43.29,0:27:46.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Hence, he switches to off-time mode.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:46.75,0:27:51.49,Default,,0,0,0,,Tonari No Totoro, Totoro~!
Dialogue: 0,0:27:51.49,0:27:55.09,Default,,0,0,0,,He might be relaxing in the living room.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:55.40,0:27:58.54,Default,,0,0,0,,This makes me remember the time I got bullied in Amagasaki.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:58.54,0:28:03.43,Default,,0,0,0,,I'd get locked up in narrow spaces like this.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:03.69,0:28:05.94,Default,,0,0,0,,I've been confined like this before.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:05.94,0:28:14.54,Default,,0,0,0,,I also remember ... a murder ... happening right before my eyes.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:14.54,0:28:16.98,Default,,0,0,0,,What are you talking about?!
Dialogue: 0,0:28:17.80,0:28:21.02,Default,,0,0,0,,10h 30min since the start.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:21.31,0:28:27.66,Default,,0,0,0,,As Kuro-chan is convinced the project is over ...
Dialogue: 0,0:28:27.66,0:28:31.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Welcome to my evening routine, the Kuro-chan livestream~!
Dialogue: 0,0:28:32.46,0:28:36.00,Default,,0,0,0,,He starts livestreaming on TikTok.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:36.43,0:28:40.11,Default,,0,0,0,,"You look like Cromartie", aah it's a homerun to be compared to a Giants player!
Dialogue: 0,0:28:40.11,0:28:43.60,Default,,0,0,0,,"Your face is too close", are you shy of faces?
Dialogue: 0,0:28:43.60,0:28:45.20,Default,,0,0,0,,"Shiro-chan", wrong, it's "Kuro"!
Dialogue: 0,0:28:45.20,0:28:47.89,Default,,0,0,0,,Who'd wanna watch Kuro-chan?!
Dialogue: 0,0:28:47.89,0:28:55.98,Default,,0,0,0,,"What are you into lately?". I'm too embarrassed to tell, but thanks for the flowers and heart-piipii~! Baby-tappii~!
Dialogue: 0,0:28:55.98,0:28:59.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Kuro-chan, stop talking ...
Dialogue: 0,0:28:58.70,0:29:02.33,Comments,,0,0,0,,Is he crying?!
Dialogue: 0,0:28:59.63,0:29:00.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Kuro-chan ...
Dialogue: 0,0:29:01.26,0:29:05.91,Default,,0,0,0,,This hellish livestream continues for 40 minutes.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:03.93,0:29:09.31,Comments,,0,0,0,,"Hell". - Well they're not wrong.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:05.91,0:29:09.31,Default,,0,0,0,,"You're a baby", that's how my parents see me. Baboo~!
Dialogue: 0,0:29:09.31,0:29:13.17,Default,,0,0,0,,"I like a guy who's just like you". You shouldn't like anyone apart from me!
Dialogue: 0,0:29:13.17,0:29:15.09,Default,,0,0,0,,His fast talking is making me insane.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:15.09,0:29:18.17,Default,,0,0,0,,It's like a cult leader chanting spells.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:18.46,0:29:21.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Chance's stress is hitting its limits.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:21.84,0:29:25.75,Default,,0,0,0,,This would make anyone go insane. - The stress of the narrow place is getting to him!
Dialogue: 0,0:29:26.06,0:29:28.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Kuro-chan, shut up already! Phwgh!!!
Dialogue: 0,0:29:29.14,0:29:32.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Tomorrow, do you ... - Shut up, Kuro-chan!!
Dialogue: 0,0:29:32.93,0:29:35.67,Comments,,0,0,0,,Some kind of noise.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:32.29,0:29:34.09,Default,,0,0,0,,Hm?
Dialogue: 0,0:29:34.49,0:29:40.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Tomorrow, do you ... - Shut up, Kuro-chan!!
Dialogue: 0,0:29:41.14,0:29:42.43,Default,,0,0,0,,Hm?
Dialogue: 0,0:29:42.43,0:29:45.77,Comments,,0,0,0,,You'll be caught! - This is scary!
Dialogue: 0,0:29:47.29,0:29:48.69,Default,,0,0,0,,This is bad!
Dialogue: 0,0:29:46.60,0:29:51.34,Comments,,0,0,0,,This must be scary for his viewers.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:48.69,0:29:51.34,Default,,0,0,0,,A major blunder by Chance!
Dialogue: 0,0:29:51.34,0:29:56.63,Default,,0,0,0,,His voice reached Kuro-chan in the room next door.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:56.63,0:30:03.17,Comments,,0,0,0,,Scary! - Especially for his viewers.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:03.17,0:30:06.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Sorry, my bad, it was nothing-dashiiin~!
Dialogue: 0,0:30:06.17,0:30:08.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Thanks for the gift, Kagetora!
Dialogue: 0,0:30:07.59,0:30:12.14,Comments,,0,0,0,,One of the comments says "Wednesday's Downtown".
Dialogue: 0,0:30:08.51,0:30:12.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Then, as he ends the livestream ...
Dialogue: 0,0:30:12.14,0:30:14.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you-dashiiin~!
Dialogue: 0,0:30:15.29,0:30:18.91,Default,,0,0,0,,There really was a noise just now!
Dialogue: 0,0:30:19.46,0:30:24.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Is there still someone there? Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:30:26.60,0:30:29.27,Default,,0,0,0,,There was a noise, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:30:40.03,0:30:44.73,Default,,0,0,0,,Ah! Who are you? Who?!
Dialogue: 0,0:30:45.00,0:30:49.27,Default,,0,0,0,,Eh, aren't you Chance Oshiro?!
Dialogue: 0,0:30:50.53,0:30:52.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Ugh, sorry ...
Dialogue: 0,0:30:52.57,0:30:56.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Why are you here a second time?!
Dialogue: 0,0:30:56.30,0:31:00.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Eh wait, so it was never over? It's not over at all?
Dialogue: 0,0:31:00.80,0:31:02.93,Default,,0,0,0,,It's not over at all?!
Dialogue: 0,0:31:02.93,0:31:07.57,Default,,0,0,0,,This is bad, now I'm the only one left.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:07.57,0:31:11.69,Default,,0,0,0,,What's this about? This was your second time, wasn't it?!
Dialogue: 0,0:31:12.03,0:31:14.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Please tell me there's no one left!
Dialogue: 0,0:31:14.83,0:31:17.27,Default,,0,0,0,,There still is someone~!
Dialogue: 0,0:31:17.73,0:31:25.23,Default,,0,0,0,,And so, just to be sure, he checks every place for a second time.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:26.20,0:31:27.97,Default,,0,0,0,,This is impossible.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:27.97,0:31:30.83,Default,,0,0,0,,If they can revive, I'm stuck in an infinite loop!
Dialogue: 0,0:31:30.83,0:31:34.17,Default,,0,0,0,,He doesn't check under the bed ...
Dialogue: 0,0:31:34.17,0:31:36.87,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm going to bed!
Dialogue: 0,0:31:37.20,0:31:39.85,Default,,0,0,0,,And then ...
Dialogue: 0,0:31:40.33,0:31:46.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Kuro-chan retires for the night.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:48.57,0:31:56.50,Default,,0,0,0,,With this, Sakai has entered a time where he can focus entirely on increasing his prize money!
Dialogue: 0,0:31:57.17,0:32:00.73,Default,,0,0,0,,However, 30 minutes later ...
Dialogue: 0,0:32:04.67,0:32:09.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Sakai has fallen asleep.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:05.57,0:32:13.33,Comments,,0,0,0,,You're kidding! - It's a bunk bed of hell!
Dialogue: 0,0:32:13.33,0:32:20.07,Comments,,0,0,0,,What kind of image is this? - How can he sleep there?!
Dialogue: 0,0:32:16.37,0:32:22.82,Default,,0,0,0,,For one hour, they both sleep soundly, snoring both above and below the bed.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:20.80,0:32:25.97,Comments,,0,0,0,,Is he serious? - What is this?!
Dialogue: 0,0:32:34.47,0:32:37.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Eh?
Dialogue: 0,0:32:37.57,0:32:44.60,Comments,,0,0,0,,That must be scary! - It might've sounded like his own snoring at first!
Dialogue: 0,0:32:44.13,0:32:47.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Scary ... ?
Dialogue: 0,0:32:55.20,0:32:57.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Eh?
Dialogue: 0,0:32:58.77,0:33:01.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Snoring?
Dialogue: 0,0:33:07.77,0:33:11.61,Default,,0,0,0,,You've gotta be kidding me.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:02.47,0:33:06.97,Comments,,0,0,0,,How can you sleep there, Sakai?!
Dialogue: 0,0:33:16.47,0:33:21.33,Default,,0,0,0,,There's someone there! Hang on, what's this about?!
Dialogue: 0,0:33:21.73,0:33:23.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Isn't that Sakai?!
Dialogue: 0,0:33:23.73,0:33:25.63,Default,,0,0,0,,You're back again?!
Dialogue: 0,0:33:25.63,0:33:28.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Wake up! Go home! Leave!
Dialogue: 0,0:33:30.53,0:33:32.27,Default,,0,0,0,,What the hell?!
Dialogue: 0,0:33:32.27,0:33:36.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Am I ... am I at Kuro-chan's place? - Of course!
Dialogue: 0,0:33:36.60,0:33:38.93,Default,,0,0,0,,Why ... ? Oh, I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:38.93,0:33:41.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Wh- ... what are you on about?!
Dialogue: 0,0:33:41.67,0:33:44.67,Default,,0,0,0,,I was scared!
Dialogue: 0,0:33:44.67,0:33:48.24,Default,,0,0,0,,You snored like crazy!
Dialogue: 0,0:33:48.60,0:33:50.85,Default,,0,0,0,,I was seriously scared!
Dialogue: 0,0:33:49.53,0:33:53.83,Comments,,0,0,0,,You snored just as loud!!
Dialogue: 0,0:33:50.85,0:33:54.38,Default,,0,0,0,,I can't get out ... - Get out! You got under there yourself, didn't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:33:54.38,0:33:57.73,Default,,0,0,0,,And I found you once before!
Dialogue: 0,0:33:57.73,0:34:00.29,Default,,0,0,0,,What the hell, leave already!!
Dialogue: 0,0:34:00.57,0:34:03.67,Default,,0,0,0,,You're noisy! - Don't tell me that, it's MY home!
Dialogue: 0,0:34:03.67,0:34:06.67,Default,,0,0,0,,You're noisy! - What's the matter with this guy?!
Dialogue: 0,0:34:06.67,0:34:09.30,Default,,0,0,0,,I just woke up, I'm in a bad mood!
Dialogue: 0,0:34:10.00,0:34:14.73,Default,,0,0,0,,And so, after a recorded 13 hours and 13 minutes, ...
Dialogue: 0,0:34:14.73,0:34:18.41,Default,,0,0,0,,... Sakai wins 402 180 yen!
Dialogue: 0,0:34:18.97,0:34:23.80,Default,,0,0,0,,This ends this tremendous project. What did you think?
Dialogue: 0,0:34:23.80,0:34:25.80,Default,,0,0,0,,What surprised me ...
Dialogue: 0,0:34:25.80,0:34:31.42,Default,,0,0,0,,... is how there are actually people who tip Kuro-chan in his livestream. - There are!
Dialogue: 0,0:34:31.42,0:34:34.62,Default,,0,0,0,,He had like hundreds of rose gifts. - Right!
Dialogue: 0,0:34:34.62,0:34:36.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Sumire, your thoughts?
Dialogue: 0,0:34:36.20,0:34:41.20,Default,,0,0,0,,I think if it had been me, I would've fainted! - Since you sleep alone? - Yeah!
Dialogue: 0,0:34:41.53,0:34:45.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Unfortunately they caught Koishida straight away. - Yes, my dad got caught right away!
Dialogue: 0,0:34:45.83,0:34:47.97,Default,,0,0,0,,What about Matsumoto?
Dialogue: 0,0:34:47.97,0:34:53.74,Default,,0,0,0,,They should've added Yaguchi as a contestant. - With the closet and all.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:47.97,0:34:53.74,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fs52.5\pos(723.6,889.8)}[Referring to an incident where Yaguchi Marika cheated on her husband and hid her lover in a closet when he returned]

